netInt.utilities.mapping

Class NumericalCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • netInt.utilities.mapping.NumericalCollection

  • public class NumericalCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    This collection stores pairs of attribute names and associated float values. The storage structure is a TreeMap with instances of String as keys, and of Float as values.
    Author:
    jsalam
